{"tid":428394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港快運駕駛艙驚現「符咒」","createTime":"2017-10-08T04:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T05:13:54.000Z","uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"116fd3191c056f7009f30de7c2978e2feb6b1369","tid":428394,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"國慶及中秋長假期開始，廉航香港快運（HK Express）卻取消十八班航班，爆出大鑊嘢。不只受影響的二千多個旅客怨聲載道，還驚動政府兩個局長譴責，影響香港國際聲譽，今次真係失禮！<br />\n<br />\nHK Express胡亂調動航班早有「前科」。小宗都聽到唔少朋友投訴，有個話航班本來下午四點起飛，點知延遲到晚上九點多！跟HK Express櫃枱職員投訴，職員話自己只是屬於代理公司。<br />\n<br />\n另一單仲離譜，HK Express擅自把大機轉為細機，令幾十人未能上機。小宗老友話上機時，竟然見到駕駛艙頂貼着一道黃色的符！他不屑地說：「揸飛機要靠嗰道符就死啦！」哈，想靠道符就鎮住個艙，呢個世界有咁廉價嘅風水布局嘅咩？咪慳得就慳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171006/552901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171006%2F552901&d=Gp3N7XiJnKaECqdxuxeLTMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=74f517cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171006%2F552901&h=f9f1db8a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171006/552901</a>"},{"pid":"e45c6c5d5e68fb5f6c68b587530d16808a06dc2b","tid":428394,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"HX D 機都有<br />\n班鬼佬屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b09126f397cacff08e0807e2fcc56ff21dc5017","tid":428394,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d1aaaa2b8d98daefc1a68689e34bb9e2b4e5221","tid":428394,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}